# Vendored verbatim (concatenated, unmodified) from
# https://github.com/eyereasoner/eye/blob/master/reasoning/restpath/initial.n3
# and
# https://github.com/eyereasoner/eye/blob/master/reasoning/restpath/path-9-3.n3
# (no truncation needed -- both upstream files are already small; 145 + 3
# lines). Distinct mechanism from any of the 15 previously-vendored cases:
# a *10-deep chain* of independent forward `=>` rules (`ex:rel1` triggers a
# rule deriving `ex:rel2` facts, which triggers a rule deriving `ex:rel3`,
# ... through `ex:rel10`, whose consequent finally derives the goal
# predicate `ex:relGoal`), stress-testing fixpoint-loop chaining depth --
# distinct from `deep_taxonomy`/`edt` (which chain a single repeated
# `subClassOf`-style predicate through instance/class facts, not 10
# independently-named predicates each requiring its own rule to fire) and
# from `backward_more`/`peano` (backward `<=` chaining, not forward `=>`).
# Confirmed by actually running `TripleStore::materialize()` on this exact
# concatenation: it derives `<x> ex:relGoal <y>` (matching the real upstream
# `reasoning/restpath/goal.n3` query/expected fact) from the sole ground
# input fact `<x> ex:rel1 <y>`.
@prefix ex: <http://example.org/#>.

<x> ex:rel1 <y>.
@prefix http: <http://www.w3.org/2011/http#>.

{
    ?a1 ex:rel1 ?b1.
}
=>
{
    ?request http:methodName "GET".
    ?request http:requestURI ?a1.
    ?request http:resp ?resp.
    ?resp http:body ?b1.
    ?a1 ex:rel2 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel2 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel2 ?b3.
}.

{
    ?a1 ex:rel2 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel2 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel2 ?b3.
}
=>
{
    ?request http:methodName "GET".
    ?request http:requestURI ?a1.
    ?request http:resp ?resp.
    ?resp http:body ?b1.
    ?a1 ex:rel3 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel3 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel3 ?b3.
}.

{
    ?a1 ex:rel3 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel3 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel3 ?b3.
}
=>
{
    ?request http:methodName "GET".
    ?request http:requestURI ?a1.
    ?request http:resp ?resp.
    ?resp http:body ?b1.
    ?a1 ex:rel4 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel4 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel4 ?b3.
}.

{
    ?a1 ex:rel4 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel4 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel4 ?b3.
}
=>
{
    ?request http:methodName "GET".
    ?request http:requestURI ?a1.
    ?request http:resp ?resp.
    ?resp http:body ?b1.
    ?a1 ex:rel5 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel5 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel5 ?b3.
}.

{
    ?a1 ex:rel5 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel5 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel5 ?b3.
}
=>
{
    ?request http:methodName "GET".
    ?request http:requestURI ?a1.
    ?request http:resp ?resp.
    ?resp http:body ?b1.
    ?a1 ex:rel6 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel6 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel6 ?b3.
}.

{
    ?a1 ex:rel6 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel6 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel6 ?b3.
}
=>
{
    ?request http:methodName "GET".
    ?request http:requestURI ?a1.
    ?request http:resp ?resp.
    ?resp http:body ?b1.
    ?a1 ex:rel7 ?b1.
    ?a2 ex:rel7 ?b2.
    ?a3 ex:rel7 ?b3.
}.

{
